data.description: Discover a beautiful move-in ready home in the desirable Vinsanto community. This single-family residence features 3 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a front gated patio overlooking the community park. The first floor offers a bedroom, guest bathroom, and laundry room. The main level boasts a spacious kitchen with an island, dining room, and a living room with built-in desks. Upstairs, you'll find two master bedrooms with bathrooms and a walk-in closet. The home is adorned with new vinyl wood flooring throughout main living areas. Enjoy the community amenities including playgrounds, walking paths, and a swimming pool.
